data.description: **On a Private Road...GPS will stop halfway down the street, please keep going and you will see the home with a for sale sign out front!** Welcome to your forever home! This charming property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, along with an additional versatile room suitable for an office, game room,  another bedroom, etc. Situated on nearly an acre of land, this home offers a plethora of amenities, including a storage shed, hot tub, and a spacious garage. Bread and Cheese Brook runs through the conservation land behind the property, so you can enjoy the scenery from the comfort of your home. Completely renovated in 2010, everything in this home is practically brand new and meticulously maintained by the current owners. Don't let this opportunity slip away to own a stunning, move-in ready property in desirable Westport!
